African Investors agree that fast-tracking the African Union’s 5% infrastructure agenda is critical in the fight against COVID-19. The AI’s African Sovereign Wealth and Pension fund leaders forum, which is part of the COVID-19 round table, met to discuss the role and response of institutional investors to the pandemic. The big question is where must the money be invested. To tell us more about this is Hubert Danso, Chairman of African Union’s Continental Business Network. For more news, visit sabcnews.com and also #SABCNews, #Coronavirus, #COVID19 on Social Media.  